   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The Nigeria Joint Response 4 supports lifesaving activities and alleviates suffering. This will be done through integrated and coordinated humanitarian responses, focusing on the most vulnerable people and enhance access to humanitarian assistance and protection services through principles humanitarian action.</narrative>
